description: BBQ for one and all is what you'll find on this Kansas food truck!This is some serious down-home cooking, made from the finest ingredients in all of Kansas, from the fresh and tender ribs to the perfect blend of spices that give every bite that perfect burst of flavor. Whether you're on the move or looking for the perfect people to cater your next big event, Drew-B-Que BBQ is the truck for you!
name: Drew-B-Que BBQ & Catering
